{"tid":1430641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【勿做標題黨】休息是為了走更長的路","createTime":"2019-08-07T19:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T20:30:43.000Z","uid":127735,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0e4f28dcd11ed2bca3074dfc798bcd03f7b885e2","tid":1430641,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:39:45.000Z","msg":"7/8/2019 呢一晚係香港人係極權政府中渡過得最開心既一晚，即使你身在現場，抑或是睇Live都可以感受到當中既氣氛，同九十年代果陣好似，講真果時我仲未出世。<br />\n<br />\n生於 1997 年既我，唔知點解可以感受得到當年港英政府既風情，我唔知咁樣形容是對或是錯，但總之共匪搶左香港之後就無再見到類似既民間自發活動，宜家可以一覽確實係小弟之幸。<br />\n<br />\n雖然時間只係短短幾個鐘，但已經可以帶出香港人既溫情同幽默。係大家訓一晚後，我地就要繼續起裝上路，繼續開拓出我地既道路，勿忘五大（或七大）訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b96ead623c8650d5fa97bb0a50208efde6d7cd26","tid":1430641,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:40:49.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"93ab004f79b07570d69a702bbb9b48e6bc340c12","tid":1430641,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:41:03.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"daf56ded1676081689f6e9d9c21c1191994da17c","tid":1430641,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:41:31.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"b8d32fc3ebe9fdeb6f9baf2a7527fff4e7095830","tid":1430641,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:42:02.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"56b1b1b41d799b5ac194f6c8638b178f84559b2d","tid":1430641,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:42:27.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"e5275bc440afe7387d0ff75315333955e73348be","tid":1430641,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:42:44.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"6b7c950136fc5785787548ed29f13cd8c2a7e4a0","tid":1430641,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:42:52.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"2242cbbb200770728aebe73bea9dc5ac7f935947","tid":1430641,"uid":127735,